anyway.

27:06.861 --> 27:09.763
- Amy insisted.
- She's a weird child.

27:09.797 --> 27:11.265
Laney.

27:21.475 --> 27:23.277
All right, well, I guess
we'll cover this later.

27:23.310 --> 27:24.712
- Okay.
- Sorry.

27:27.815 --> 27:30.417
- What is she up to?
- Oh, give 'em a break.

27:30.451 --> 27:32.386
- They're a cute couple.
- It's not so fun

27:32.419 --> 27:34.388
when it's your party, is it?

27:34.421 --> 27:37.258
Ah, could you go get the cake,
please.

27:43.898 --> 27:48.836
Uh, go sit over there, come on.

27:53.774 --> 27:55.142
I'm Bryn, by the way.

27:55.176 --> 27:57.044
Oh, sorry, Josh.

27:57.077 --> 27:59.413
And you've met Laney,
our neighbor's daughter.

27:59.446 --> 28:01.982
But she's here so much, she's
like family.

28:02.016 --> 28:04.351
