40:42.043 --> 40:43.010
- Josh.
- Josh.

40:43.044 --> 40:45.478
Yes, hi, I'm a, I'm a fan.

40:45.513 --> 40:46.747
- You don't say.
- Yes, no.

40:46.781 --> 40:49.150
I was only nine years old the
first time I saw you conduct.

40:49.183 --> 40:52.253
