the Hall.

40:52.286 --> 40:55.990
And I just, I used to
pretend to be you.

40:56.023 --> 40:57.124
I would set up stuffed animals

40:57.158 --> 40:58.960
and have them be my orchestra.

40:58.993 --> 41:02.797
So I just, I just love
you in a very platonic

41:04.598 --> 41:07.635
just sort of admiration
kind of, kind of way.

41:09.303 --> 41:11.005
- Well, well, thank you.
- Yeah.

41:11.038 --> 41:12.673
Thank you, why don't
you kids stick around.

41:12.707 --> 41:13.941
We can always use some more
voices.

41:13.975 --> 41:16.777
