- Oh, that's right.

41:20.848 --> 41:21.882
The party, I forgot.

41:21.916 --> 41:23.684
I wish I could attend.

41:23.718 --> 41:26.087
Well, look out for her tonight.

41:26.120 --> 41:27.955
- We will.
- Oh, I was talking about you.

41:30.558 --> 41:32.026
- All right, go.
- Pleasure, sir.

41:32.059 --> 41:33.928
Oh my pleasure, thank you.

41:33.961 --> 41:35.596
- Bye, honey, bye, honey.
- Thank you.

41:35.629 --> 41:37.698
- Thank you.
- See you.

41:37.732 --> 41:41.869
Great job, thanks.

41:41.902 --> 41:46.574
♪ Call out, call out ♪

41:46.607 --> 41:48.109
