42:53.307 --> 42:57.978
Welcome to our somewhat
famous alt classical enclave.

43:01.415 --> 43:02.783
What are you doing?

43:02.817 --> 43:04.819
And what are you talking
about?

43:04.852 --> 43:05.853
Who is he?

43:06.555 --> 43:08.656
- Just a friend.
- Holy crap.

43:08.689 --> 43:09.957
- He's the guy.
- No.

43:09.990 --> 43:11.392
The guy from the competition
tomorrow.

43:11.425 --> 43:13.194
The guy that you've been
stalking.

43:13.227 --> 43:14.328
No, I wasn't stalking him.

43:14.361 --> 43:17.665
Are you purposely trying
to sabotage the poor kid?

43:17.698 --> 43:19.366
I was just curious, don't be
weird.

43:19.400 --> 43:22.970
Hey, hey, what's been going on
with you?

43:25.840 --> 43:29.176
I kinda don't wanna do the
competition.

43:30.377 --> 43:33.247
