your fingers chopped off.

43:37.051 --> 43:38.886
This time, it's different.

43:38.919 --> 43:41.322
He's really good, like really
good.

43:41.355 --> 43:43.190
Why do you care about
the competition at all?

43:43.224 --> 43:45.326
You can just quit.

43:45.359 --> 43:46.227
Grandma.

43:47.862 --> 43:50.364
I'm sorry, sweetie, you are so
screwed.

