- All right, everyone.
- Woo!

43:55.703 --> 43:56.670
- Yeah!
- Woo!

43:56.704 --> 43:58.739
Let's get this thing rolling.

45:37.938 --> 45:40.908
Woo!

45:40.941 --> 45:43.043
- Woo, all right!
- Woo!

45:43.077 --> 45:44.778
- Yeah!
- All right!

45:45.913 --> 45:47.881
- Let's do it again!
- Yeah!

45:52.286 --> 45:53.420
- Whoo!
- Whoo!

45:56.056 --> 45:57.291
Goodnight.

45:57.324 --> 45:59.460
See you next week.

